name: Penny, the HEN bot
description:
Penny was the one very first assistant to Rafael Lima. During the creation of hic et nunc platform, most of the common works he gave to this cute robot. But after success and increasing amount of real people, working on this project, he just dumped Penny. Now the HEN bot living on abandoned beach with all memories, related to this fine period of time. 
Take him to your wallet, give him some love.
Thanks to TaraNC
